These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: spinach, corn
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person eating corn##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | corn   | spinach  |
| Sport   | cycling | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, potato
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person eating potato##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | lime | potato      |
| Pet    | chinchilla  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
