.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, dancer
2 different pets are kept: rat, dog
1. the teacher is in an odd position##4
2. the teacher is not the owner of the dog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | teacher | dancer |
| Pet   | rat       | dog       |

